 Type of list in html ?
    1.UL - unorder list
        type
           1. disc
           2. square
           3. cricle
           4. none 

   2. OL - order list 
        type
           1. type="1"
           2. type="A"
           3. type="a"
           4. type="I"
           5. type="i"

  3. DL - definition list 
        dt - definition title  - it use to display headline of Content
        dd - definition details - it use to display about the contents
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  DETAILS & SUMMARY
=> details & summary - use to toggle the text for read more and read less.
