 => Table in html
    1. Frist method of table - not supported with angular and react
       =>table 
           ->caption
           ->tr - table row 
                -> th - table heading
                -> td - table data

    2. Second method of table - supported with angular and react
      =>table
        ->thead - it cover upper section of table
              ->tr 
                 ->th

        ->tbody - it cover middle/ data part
             ->tr
                 ->td

       ->tfoot - it cover bottom of table
              ->tr
                 ->th

  => property in table,tr, th.], td, thead, tbody, tfoot
          ->align - left, center, right
          ->border -
          ->bordercolor -
          ->cellpadding - it apply space inside th & td
          ->cellspacing - it apply space outside th & td
          
    ->table1.html
       ->colspan - it use to combine space of 2 0r more columns th, td ( it combine left to right)
       ->rowspan - it combine space of 2 or more tr (top of bottom)
    ->table3.html
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   input tags
       ->text    ]
       ->number  ] - single line 
       ->email   ]
       ->password ]
       ->date     ] - slect
       ->file     ]
       ->select   ]
       ->textarea ] - multiple
       ->radio    ] - user can only select one
       ->checkbox ] - user can select one or more
       ->button
               ->submit
               ->reset 
               ->button - need javascript

   property in input tags / element 
   ->placeholder - it is for input guidance
   ->maxlength - it set max inout limit in "text, password, email, textarea".
   ->size - it resize width of "text, password, email".
   -> name - it use to  capture value given by user in html 
   ->readonly - it will make input element as readonly but value can pass to backend
   ->disabled -it will make input element as readonly but value can not pass to backend
   ->value -it use to display default value in input element 
   ->tabindex -it use to set sequence of cursor 
   ->required -it make input element as mandatory to fill
   ->selected -it make option as default option in select   
   ->checked -it make checkbox, radio default checked
   
   ->form tag
   ->it is parent container of all input 
   ->the property are 
        1. action- it use to set backend url where the form data get submitted
        2. method- it define type of communication as secure or un-secure 
           a. get - it is un-secure because it pass from browser url.
           b. post - it is secure, data will not be visible anywhere
           c. patch - patch upadate on changes
           d. put - put upadte changes and non changes values
           e. delete - it send request to delete record from server

        3. enctype
           ->it use to encode any type attachment

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
    Type of target in html herf?
      target="_self"  -  it open next page in same tab.
      target="_blank" - it open next page in new tab on every click.
      target="_new"   - it open next page in new tab but only at first click.
